text: Yakhana nabi tamra ekajana strira kache ekati katha gopane balalena, atahpara stri yakhana ta bale dila ebam allaha nabike ta janiye dilena, takhana nabi se bisaye strike kichu balalena ebam kichu balalena na. Nabi yakhana ta strike balalena, takhana stri balalenah ke apanake e samparke abahita karala? Nabi balalena,h yini sarbajna, oyakiphahala, tini amake abahita karechena.
